reviewText: I have many travel videos on Hawaii, but this 210 minutes long 2 DVD set is the best I have seen. It features all six islands and gives an extensive history of each island, including the attack on Pearl Harbor, the leper colony established by Father Damien and the products that the islands produce.
Was all about Hawaii,Beautiful scenery . If you like something like a history lesson then this is for you. Explains all the history behind all the islands.

I don't know if I'll ever go to Hawaii or not, but this 2 disc set gives an excellent overview. Disc one is the scenic side of Hawaii, showing beautiful highlights of each island. It's pretty in depth, and informative.

Disc two is the history lesson. this part is extremely good, and informative. If you've always wanted to know the history of Hawaii (2 hrs), and / or want a good travel log (90 min.), this is the one to buy.
